 yogurt.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/07/sausage-pepper-pasta/?replytocom=82714#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-82714\", \"82714\", \"respond\", \"17695\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-82717\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/064de9c066c71184f6c0df42d28b4a52?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\">yousuf</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/07/sausage-pepper-pasta/#comment-82717\">07.08.13 at 9:24 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>fyi &#8211; garlic is included in the ingredients but not in the instructions. recipe looks great!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/07/sausage-pepper-pasta/?replytocom=82717#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-82717\", \"82717\", \"respond\", \"17695\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<ul class=\"children\">\n\n\t<li class=\"comment byuser comment-author-beth bypostauthor odd alt depth-2\" id=\"comment-82719\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/254ccb2a309b73f73d1c117c28ea4d03?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.budgetbytes.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Beth M</a>